<br>
if you are a growing guild, you should try to equip some key ppl that show to all raid(war, cleric, shammy and chanter). then you will be able to raid more easily and get more loot. on my side, i would have award to your warrior if he is always on cuz more AC/HP he got, better it is for your cleric. that mean less heal and easier to tank mobs.<br>
