<br>
I am in a guild which has recently moved from a merit based system (where loot was awared to ppl on a NBG basis by the officers) to a Point based system (where points are awarded for each raid u attend.<br>
<br>
It has made a major positive impact on the guild, Dramatically increased raid attendance, and we have moved on to much harder targets in a very short space of time.<br>
<br>
This is simply because our raid attendance has increased so much.<br>
<br>
I would definetly recommend you look into this option.<br>
<br>
<br>
