<br>
Random drops, but modify each person's random by the number of usable items they lost out on - subtract x number of items from the person's current tally when awarded an item.<br>
<br>
5 plate classes are on a raid and a plate item drops, they each random for it - however person 1 and 2 have seen 4 and 5 drops that they haven't won and they'd random like:<br>
<br>
1: /ran 40 140<br>
2: /ran 50 150<br>
3-5: /ran 100<br>
<br>
Simple system that rewards the people who show up continually, without getting too bogged down in the intricacies of a full blown DKP system. Could also just have the officers decide on loot though, that's what has worked for us since early Velious. <p><big><center><b><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=19405 target=blank>Marshall Sscaley Iceblade</a><br><i><a href=http://companions.windsofstorm.net>The Companions ~ Team Headstart</a></i> <br>
